article.description: — Jackson Stormo scored 18 points as Siena beat Canisius 73-66 on Thursday night.
article.headline: Stormo, Camper lift Siena over Canisius 73-66
article.linkText: Stormo, Camper lift Siena over Canisius 73-66
article.story: ALBANY, N.Y. -- — Jackson Stormo scored 18 points as Siena beat Canisius 73-66 on Thursday night. Manny Camper added 17 points, Jordan King scored 15 and Jalen Pickett had 15 for the Saints (12-3, 12-3 Metro Atlantic Athletic Conference). Camper also had 11 rebounds, while Pickett posted seven rebounds and six assists. Malek Green had 21 points for the Golden Griffins (6-5, 6-5). Majesty Brandon added 12 points. Armon Harried had six rebounds. ------ For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP--Top25 ------ This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
